* Large file support
* fixes an issue regarding binary constants

1.0.1 [2011-07-12]
* minor changes

1.0 [2010-11-05]
* Offers to overwrite destination file
* Piping in otrkeys using tail -f now works
* Nicer error messages ;-)

0.9 [2010-10-17]
* otrtool -h slimmed down to "important" commands

